---
title: Quick Beef Koftas & Cucumber Ribbon Couscous with Flaked Almonds & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Spice up your mealtime with beef koftas! Juicy, savoury and packed with flavour, these bundles of joy go perfectly with a vibrant couscous salad and tangy garlic yoghurt. Load up your plate and dig in.

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with pearl couscous
due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
